Multiprocess Commmunication Library
===================================

Multiprocess commmunication library (MCL) is a set of python modules for
implementing the publish-subscribe message passing paradigm in multiprocess
systems.

Requirements
------------

MCL has been written for use on Linux systems. The following libraries are
required (on Debian-based distributions):

* python-msgpack

Installation
------------

The package can be installed using::

    sudo pip install .

Support
------------

If you find a bug, please report the issue to::

    a.bender@acfr.usyd.edu.au
